# pexip_infinity_gms_gateway_token (Resource)

Manages the Google Meet gateway token configuration with the Infinity service. This is a singleton resource - only one GMS gateway token configuration exists per system.

## Example Usage

```terraform
resource "pexip_infinity_gms_gateway_token" "example" {
  certificate = file("${path.module}/certificates/gms.crt")
  private_key = var.gms_private_key
}
```


